<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="future-n">future <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'fjuːtʃə(r)/    美 /'fjuːtʃər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-u-the">1.★ <strong>[U] [与the连用] 将来；未来：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Don't think too much about past troubles — look to the future.
别多想过去的烦恼，向前看。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>What will the cities of <strong>the future</strong> look like?
未来的城市会是什么样子呢？</p></div>

<h4 id="2-c">2.★ <strong>[C] 前途；前景：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>His future looked bright.
他的前途看起来一片光明。</p><footer>北师大⑦ – 21</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She <strong>has a great future</strong> ahead of her.
她前程远大。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="in-future">in future</h3>
<p>1.<strong>今后：</strong><br />
from now on：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>If you can just help me out this time, I promise I'll be more careful in future.
只要这次你能帮我，我保证以后会更加小心。</p></div>

<h3 id="in-the-near-future">in the (near) future</h3>
<p>1.<strong>在 (不久的) 将来</strong><br />
soon：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>No one can tell what will happen in the future.
没人能说准将来会发生什么事。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The film market may witness a slowdown in the near future.
在不久的将来电影市场也许会萎缩。</p><footer>2016 江苏书面表达</footer></div>

<h3 id="have-a-no-future">have a / no future</h3>
<p>1.<strong>有 / 没有前途；有 / 没有未来：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Our world has a future only if people learn to conserve nature and not waste energy.
人们只有学会保护自然和节约能源，我们的世界才会有未来。</p><footer>外研⑤ – 6</footer></div>

<h3 id="there-is-a-no-future-in-sth">there is a / no future in sth</h3>
<p>1.<strong>某事有 / 没有前途：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He felt there was no future in farming.
他觉得务农没有前途。</p></div></div>